                             From ABQ to Los Alamos
   __________________________________________________________________

   Visitors typically drive from the Albuquerque Airport (ABQ) to Los
   Alamos. From the aiport, take I25 north to Santa Fe. At Santa Fe, take
   the St. Francis Drive exit (US 285) through town, following the signs
   for "Los Alamos/Taos/Espanola".

   Approximately 20 miles north of Santa Fe, you will reach Pojaque. Take
   the exit to Los Alamos, US 502. This exit is from the right lane, but
   then you turn left under an underpass. After another 15 minutes, you
   will need to follow the signs to the Los Alamos town site (left lane).
   This will take you into the town, where the local hotels are.

   The total driving time is approximately 2 hours.
